data.description: Rare opportunity to own this Asian influenced masterpiece of architecture and Japanese design. This mid century 5/4 is one of the last great vintage 70's homes maintained in impeccable condition.  From the imported New Zealand blue metal tile roof to the Zen waterfalls and gardens to the intimate courtyard pool, this property could easily be a paradigmatic trophy home or investment for the right buyer.  Nestled on a huge corner, half acre+ lot, the horseshoe interior flow highlights the private dining and office, shoji doors, stove pipe fireplace and sunken bar.    Motivated seller will consider all serious offers.   Wholesale private financing rates available for qualified buyers as low as 5%.
